uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.alignment

Class ProfileBinTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      • uk.ac.ebi.masscascade.alignment.ProfileBinTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<ProfileBin>, javax.swing.table.TableModel

    public class ProfileBinTableModel
extends javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
implements java.lang.Iterable<ProfileBin>
    Table model for arranging multiple profile containers in a JTable . The profiles in the containers are grouped by their m/z and retention time values based on the given tolerance values.
